{"tid":424901,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞措詞一問","createTime":"2017-10-05T07:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T17:37:12.000Z","uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee671a7a5678c1a699a3321a9d54a17675a0137","tid":424901,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"港女與內地夫吵架後墮樓亡　遺1個月大B女<br />\n<br />\n與內地男結婚的姓林(32歲)香港女子，月前誕下女兒後，疑患上產後抑鬱，今晨她疑與丈夫透過電話爭吵，至下午2時許，趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">外孫女</span>到醫院探病時，由將軍澳尚德邨尚信樓13樓住所墮樓，倒臥４樓平台一間幼稚園對開，救護員到場證實她已死亡。<br />\n<br />\n首先，RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。<br />\n<br />\n其次，睇哩段文字嘅時候，好疑惑「外孫女」哩個詞，明明係講緊死者個女。<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係用 外孫女/ 其女/ 稚女/ 幼女 定係乜名好？"},{"pid":"d2c49d43064c33949489c92558256da2623870e6","tid":424901,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"佢想講係「其母」既外孫女"},{"pid":"63e8b845c3c5d05d78da630f5f6750bcd607b3a0","tid":424901,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢想講係「其母」既外孫女</blockquote><br />\n我明個意思 但咁講唔會太曲折咩"},{"pid":"4a31a2fe2b42e8dbe338a523ef8da94031188d8e","tid":424901,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢想講係「其母」既外孫女</blockquote><br />\n我明個意思 但咁講唔會太曲折咩</blockquote><br />\n首先, 稚女/ 幼女呢兩個詞都係用嚟形容細路女, 但冇指明關係<br />\n<blockquote>趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">稚女</span>到醫院探病<br />\n趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">幼女</span>到醫院探病</blockquote><br />\n呢兩句話死者呀媽帶住街邊求其一個細路女都解得通, 表達唔到個細路女係死者個女(當然睇上文下理都知係死者個女)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;其女&quot;都係唔得<br />\n<blockquote>趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">其女</span>到醫院探病</blockquote><br />\n因為咁樣就變成死者母親帶死者到醫院探病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實原文&quot;外孫女&quot;都唔一定啱, 因為死者母親可以有好多個外孫女, 唔一定係死者個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以正確嘅寫法應該要加埋&quot;死者&quot;, 即係<br />\n<blockquote>趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">死者女兒/死者親女</span>到醫院探病</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7e22d78c61bd1ec96127d355aa4b07e9acccd4dd","tid":424901,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;其女&quot;都係唔得<br />\n<blockquote>趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">其女</span>到醫院探病</blockquote><br />\n因為咁樣就變成死者母親帶死者到醫院探病</blockquote><br />\n打完睇返其實呢度有啲唔係好肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&quot;其母&quot;同&quot;其女&quot;可以解(死者)其母帶同(死者)其女<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">死者<br />\n│<br />\n┌───┐<br />\n其母　　其女</div><br />\n<br />\n上面例句嘅解法係<br />\n[(死者)其母]帶同[其女](=死者)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">死者　　　<br />\n&darr;　　　<br />\n其母&rarr;其女</div><br />\n<br />\n有冇語言學巴絲可以講吓邊個啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e92d0fcdbafef6fb06712cc0f1325a7b37d074","tid":424901,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&quot;其女&quot;都係唔得<br />\n<blockquote>趁其母帶同<span style=\"color: red;\">其女</span>到醫院探病</blockquote><br />\n因為咁樣就變成死者母親帶死者到醫院探病</blockquote><br />\n打完睇返其實呢度有啲唔係好肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&quot;其母&quot;同&quot;其女&quot;可以解(死者)其母帶同(死者)其女<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">死者<br />\n│<br />\n┌───┐<br />\n其母　　其女</div><br />\n<br />\n上面例句嘅解法係<br />\n[(死者)其母]帶同[其女](=死者)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">死者　　　<br />\n&darr;　　　<br />\n其母&rarr;其女</div><br />\n<br />\n有冇語言學巴絲可以講吓邊個啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇傳媒人幫手解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a97064cd83f99dbc0062716912a6f910d489cd","tid":424901,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}